{"type": "article", "id": 22877, "title": "带镂空灯罩的吊灯和落地灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-26T07:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150658bJl5npQIR6BOqkWh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞典的工作室 Front 为瑞典品牌 Zero 设计的灯，有落地灯和吊灯两款，LED 灯在圆盘里，上面用 8 根细的弧形金属连接，最后收束到一起，成为一种镂空的灯罩装饰，也是轻盈而优雅的设计。落地灯的底座设计了 4 根细长支撑，下面连接了一个小圆，与上面的弧形灯罩相对，具有很强的装饰性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150657AXgpfu1vM4aHS62q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.97222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150657vNwLarCjGQ2ZMSXP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.35897436\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150658uTGJEQD0YxewcIR3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}